'''Bonobo''' ezalí [[makáko]] enɛ́nɛ eye evándaka o [[Afríka]] ya Kati, o kati ya [[Kongó-Kinsásá]].

== Epímeli mpé bojito ==
* Molaí (molómi): 75 - 90 cm
* Bojito (molómi): 39 - 45 kg
* Molaí (ebɛ́mbɛ́): 70 - 75 cm
* Bojito (ebɛ́mbɛ́): 31 - 33 kg<ref>http://www.tierenzyklopaedie.de/tiere/bonobo.html</ref>

== Kalási ==
* Kalási: ''Mammalia'' ([[Nyama ya mabɛ́lɛ]])
* *Ordre: ''Primates'' (*Primates) 			
* Libóta: ''Hominidae'' (*grands singes) 	
* *Genre: ''Pan'' ([[Mokómbósó]]) 				
* Nkómbó: ''Pan paniscus'' ('''Bonobo''')

